<Layout title="How Brisbane Property Lot Shape Affects Sale Value: Frontage, Depth and Battle-Axe Blocks | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Two Brisbane blocks of identical area can sell at very different prices because of shape. Here is how frontage, depth, and battle-axe configuration move sale value, who pays the premium, and what sellers should benchmark against." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
